      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781096749085,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How should the CandidateTrajectory Message look like?\nRequirements:\n- Visualization in rviz → Would benefit from the CandidateTrajectories message definition\n    - But: \n- Simple interaction with ToD\n\nOwn definition:\n\nCandidateTrajectories\nstd_msgs/Header\ntum_autoware_teleoperation_msgs/CandidateTrajectory [] trajectories\n\nCandidateTrajectory\nautoware_planning_msgs/msg/Trajectory trajectory\ngeometry_msgs/msg/Pose goal_pose\nstd_msgs/String identifier\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How should the CandidateTrajectory Message look like?\nRequirements:\n- Visualization in rviz → Would benefit from the CandidateTrajectories message definition\n    - But: \n- Simple interaction with ToD\n\nOwn definition:\n\nCandidateTrajectories\nstd_msgs/Header\ntum_autoware_teleoperation_msgs/CandidateTrajectory [] trajectories\n\nCandidateTrajectory\nautoware_planning_msgs/msg/Trajectory trajectory\ngeometry_msgs/msg/Pose goal_pose\nstd_msgs/String identifier\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
